簡介

	                                            Taishih Chi received the B.S. degree from National Taiwan University, Taiwan, in 1992, and the Ph.D. degrees from the University of Maryland, College Park, in 2003, all in electrical engineering. 
	                                        

	                                            He joined the Department of Communication Engineering, National Chiao Tung University, Taiwan, in July 2005. His research interests are in neuromorphic auditory modeling, soft computing, and speech/audio analysis.
	                                        






